message:
After change GPU, i have PP1V5_S0GPU_ISNS bad 0V, the board start and shutdown.
i have PP1V5_S0GPU_ISNS is not really short but 0,022 in diode mode, 0V in volt when i start the board.
i don't find where is it generate this signal, is it possible a bad GPU (1608)?
thanks
Usually fucked GPU, remove and check for short again. Also 1608 GPUs are fake.
